'''Tanga takrurant''' d [[tanga]] ig lan (yesɛan) taftart tanarumt d armeskil d asebdad, Tanga takrurant tezmer ad tili tesraw neɣ zeddig (d [[aferdis akruran|aferdis]] neɣ d [[uddis akruran|uddis]] neɣ d [[arway]], Akken daɣen tezmer ad tili deg [[Addaden n tenga|waddaden ikṛaden n tenga]] ([[Amazzal|Tamazzalt]], [[Taɣuṛi|Taqurant]] d [[Agaz|Tagazayt]]), W tezmer daɣen ad tuɣal seg yiwen ar wayeṭ deg waddaden-a s wemgarad n [[adad|wadad]] d [[taẓɣelt|teẓɣelt]]
Yal tasmekta deg yal tanga takrurant tettili dges [[takura|tkura]] yettaṭafen ideg (amkan) deg [[ilem (tasengama)|yilem]]

Ttwameggezen (twaḥsaben) [[aman|waman]] zeddigen d amedya ɣef tanga takrurant ilan (yesɛan) yiwen n wazal n Uksijin d Uhidṛujin

